  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Project Genesis is a sci-fi shooter that fuses two distinct gameplay experiences into one seamless combat loop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700240/extras/ead0316e9b462614eff911cf0fbfb4bf.poster.avif?t=1772815721\" width=600 height=126 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700240/extras/ead0316e9b462614eff911cf0fbfb4bf.webm?t=1772815721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700240/extras/ead0316e9b462614eff911cf0fbfb4bf.mp4?t=1772815721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700240/extras/c7b36fd2ff0b31faebb0f14e7395e52d.webp?t=1772815721\" width=600 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Breach and Board</strong> When ships get close enough, the Breach and Board sequence triggers a shift into FPS close-quarter combat aboard massive capital ships. Standard WASD controls make the transition seamless — no new control schemes, no perspective adjustment period.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700240/extras/7abbf600c8ecbe3b542b5327537b65f0.poster.avif?t=1772815721\" width=600 height=126 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700240/extras/7abbf600c8ecbe3b542b5327537b65f0.webm?t=1772815721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700240/extras/7abbf600c8ecbe3b542b5327537b65f0.mp4?t=1772815721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700240/extras/062a50883b4265efeadfba9736c4108c.webp?t=1772815721\" width=600 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ship to Ship Combat</strong> Engage in third-person space combat with free-look targeting. Steer your ship, aim freely, and engage enemies across open space. The flight model is intentionally accessible — no complicated controls, no steep learning curve. Targeting and HUD systems borrow from FPS industry standards to keep the experience intuitive from the first session.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700240/extras/6f0ba00bf0de2a841620332a70647275.poster.avif?t=1772815721\" width=600 height=126 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700240/extras/6f0ba00bf0de2a841620332a70647275.webm?t=1772815721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700240/extras/6f0ba00bf0de2a841620332a70647275.mp4?t=1772815721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700240/extras/be4b9b735d9695f9860b949370e492d8.webp?t=1772815721\" width=600 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Shared Control Language</strong> Across both modes, Project Genesis uses a common gameplay paradigm — HP, Energy, primary and secondary weapons, abilities and utilities — built around familiar Tank, Support, and DPS roles. Boost, shields, weapon loadouts, countermeasures, and throwable ordnance give players meaningful tactical depth without unnecessary complexity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Project Genesis was developed with an active community of Test Pilots whose feedback shaped the game's direction from the ground up. Active development has wound down, but the game remains available to those who supported it during Early Access.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700240/extras/5c2fe0546c4170752fcef490ed7d4935.poster.avif?t=1772815721\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700240/extras/5c2fe0546c4170752fcef490ed7d4935.webm?t=1772815721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700240/extras/5c2fe0546c4170752fcef490ed7d4935.mp4?t=1772815721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Project Genesis is a sci-fi shooter that fuses two distinct gameplay experiences into one seamless combat loop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700240/extras/ead0316e9b462614eff911cf0fbfb4bf.poster.avif?t=1772815721\" width=600 height=126 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700240/extras/ead0316e9b462614eff911cf0fbfb4bf.webm?t=1772815721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700240/extras/ead0316e9b462614eff911cf0fbfb4bf.mp4?t=1772815721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700240/extras/c7b36fd2ff0b31faebb0f14e7395e52d.webp?t=1772815721\" width=600 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Breach and Board</strong> When ships get close enough, the Breach and Board sequence triggers a shift into FPS close-quarter combat aboard massive capital ships. Standard WASD controls make the transition seamless — no new control schemes, no perspective adjustment period.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700240/extras/7abbf600c8ecbe3b542b5327537b65f0.poster.avif?t=1772815721\" width=600 height=126 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700240/extras/7abbf600c8ecbe3b542b5327537b65f0.webm?t=1772815721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700240/extras/7abbf600c8ecbe3b542b5327537b65f0.mp4?t=1772815721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700240/extras/062a50883b4265efeadfba9736c4108c.webp?t=1772815721\" width=600 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ship to Ship Combat</strong> Engage in third-person space combat with free-look targeting. Steer your ship, aim freely, and engage enemies across open space. The flight model is intentionally accessible — no complicated controls, no steep learning curve. Targeting and HUD systems borrow from FPS industry standards to keep the experience intuitive from the first session.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700240/extras/6f0ba00bf0de2a841620332a70647275.poster.avif?t=1772815721\" width=600 height=126 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700240/extras/6f0ba00bf0de2a841620332a70647275.webm?t=1772815721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700240/extras/6f0ba00bf0de2a841620332a70647275.mp4?t=1772815721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700240/extras/be4b9b735d9695f9860b949370e492d8.webp?t=1772815721\" width=600 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Shared Control Language</strong> Across both modes, Project Genesis uses a common gameplay paradigm — HP, Energy, primary and secondary weapons, abilities and utilities — built around familiar Tank, Support, and DPS roles. Boost, shields, weapon loadouts, countermeasures, and throwable ordnance give players meaningful tactical depth without unnecessary complexity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Project Genesis was developed with an active community of Test Pilots whose feedback shaped the game's direction from the ground up. Active development has wound down, but the game remains available to those who supported it during Early Access.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700240/extras/5c2fe0546c4170752fcef490ed7d4935.poster.avif?t=1772815721\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700240/extras/5c2fe0546c4170752fcef490ed7d4935.webm?t=1772815721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/700240/extras/5c2fe0546c4170752fcef490ed7d4935.mp4?t=1772815721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
